    "name": "阿加莎·克里斯蒂 – 尼罗河上的惨案  (Agatha Christie - Death on the Nile)",
    "steam_appid": 3150480,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3150480/extras/f273f1c34525ef36346a2d22a6960b36.poster.avif?t=1771345621\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3150480/extras/f273f1c34525ef36346a2d22a6960b36.webm?t=1771345621\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3150480/extras/f273f1c34525ef36346a2d22a6960b36.mp4?t=1771345621\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><br>在《尼罗河惨案》中，一场惨案打破了尼罗河游船之旅的平和。幸好，名侦探演赫尔克里·波洛也在船上。与此同时，为了追捕一名凶手，一位私家侦探从伦敦追到马略卡岛，又辗转前往纽约，最后来到了埃及。<br>两起调查在阿布辛贝神庙不期而遇，实力超群的侦探二人组将携手破获这起峰回路转的复杂案件。然而，故事并未止步于原著，即使是阿加莎最忠实的粉丝，也很难看透游戏内的重重谜团，猜到诸多反转。<br><br><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3150480/extras/6904137be8c809835fa18b6c35860061.poster.avif?t=1771345621\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3150480/extras/6904137be8c809835fa18b6c35860061.webm?t=1771345621\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3150480/extras/6904137be8c809835fa18b6c35860061.mp4?t=1771345621\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>双主角：扮演赫尔克里·波洛与简·罗伊斯，两位主角均拥有独特的视角与剧情，最终交织于精彩绝伦的结局中。<br></li><li>创新背景设定：沉浸于经典故事所处的绚烂多彩、活力四射的 70 年代，体验人头攒动的迪斯科舞厅，还有形形色色粉墨登场的人物。<br></li><li>扩展的故事线：投身紧随原著情节的全新调查之旅，无论是阿加莎的资深读者，还是初次接触故事的新玩家，都将收获满满的意外之喜。<br></li><li>多样化场景：从充满异域风情的尼罗河游轮，到马略卡岛、伦敦与开罗的繁华街道，这些迷人的地方会让你流连忘返。</li></ul> <br><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3150480/extras/1eacccb435fccee345429119eac8878a.poster.avif?t=1771345621\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3150480/extras/1eacccb435fccee345429119eac8878a.webm?t=1771345621\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3150480/extras/1eacccb435fccee345429119eac8878a.mp4?t=1771345621\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>增强版思维导图：收集并关联线索，在动态思维导图中进行推理，推动故事的发展。<br></li><li>质询系统：使用搜集到的证据询问嫌疑人，揭露谎言，发掘隐藏的真相。<br></li><li>角色档案：通过对话和观察收集信息，完善每名角色的详细档案。</li></ul> <br><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3150480/extras/b1ce5d37fa95cc742d948f80662b70aa.poster.avif?t=1771345621\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3150480/extras/b1ce5d37fa95cc742d948f80662b70aa.webm?t=1771345621\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3150480/extras/b1ce5d37fa95cc742d948f80662b70aa.mp4?t=1771345621\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3150480/extras/2d30181349dfa7dbc8f31c628f353375.poster.avif?t=1771345621\" width=600 height=130 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3150480/extras/2d30181349dfa7dbc8f31c628f353375.webm?t=1771345621\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3150480/extras/2d30181349dfa7dbc8f31c628f353375.mp4?t=1771345621\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
